{"tid":1313921,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家今日集中練投擲技能","createTime":"2019-07-14T03:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:14:45.000Z","uid":104454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe359ed581233c2d2737baf6e2a28d263122647","tid":1313921,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"琴日已經見到好多人都開始玩投擲技能<br />\n<br />\n係升級武力既最佳踏腳石，襯亂果時乜鳩都拋啲過去，打中班狗又冇仇報，岩哂想用武力但又唔敢咁前既巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手開頭建議玩傘，水樽先，等到熟練咗力度同距離之後就自己開始練下唔同物件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得要對準班狗，唔好打中自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:講緊魔力寶貝online"},{"pid":"f031464d6c07800cf25c93b56c99423558d15962","tid":1313921,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實飛石索係咩原理 利申玩芒亨"},{"pid":"1ce5ba1e43314055e6225b5e1a31c8e4a4a2c097","tid":1313921,"uid":104454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f031464d6c07800cf25c93b56c99423558d15962","tid":1313921,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"其實飛石索係咩原理 利申玩芒亨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7UTa4pw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7UTa4pw.jpg&h=16098f5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗純粹係轉果時令舊石唔好跌出黎/飛走 之後一下拋出去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08d936b20682d0890caaac5c3876cf60dfabcda","tid":1313921,"uid":104454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位係時候武力升級啦"},{"pid":"ebbbb46f49ae16adf5b10d9771181fb5314e1f65","tid":1313921,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:48: